 = 0.1 * (-2*1.49033674 + 4*0.35) = -0.098168468\nk3 = 0.1 * f(0.35, 1.58024216 - 0.049084234) = 0.1 * (-2*1.531157926 + 4*0.35) = -0.098231572\nk4 = 0.1 * f(0.4, 1.58024216 - 0.098231572) = 0.1 * (-2*1.482010588 + 4*0.4) = -0.0164021176\ny_4 = 1.58024216 + (-0.17981084 + 2*(-0.098168468) + 2*(-0.098231572) + (-0.0164021176)) / 6 = 1.2158179424\n\nIteration 5 (t = 0.5):\nt_4 = 0.4, y_4 = 1.2158179424\nk1 = 0.1 * f(0.4, 1.2158179424) = 0.1 * (-2*1.2158179424 + 4*0.4) = -0.0164021176\nk2 = 0.1 * f(0.45, 1.2158179424 - 0.0082010588) = 0.1 * (-2*1.2076168836 + 4*0.45) = 0.0572394324\nk3 = 0.1 * f(0.45, 1.2158179424 + 0.0028619712) = 0.1 * (-2*1.2186799136 + 4*0.45) = 0.0572000864\nk4 = 0.1 * f(0.5, 1.2158179424 + 0.0572000864) = 0.1 * (-2*1.2730180288 + 4*0.5) = 0.1263982144\ny_5 = 1.2158179424 + (-0.0164021176 + 2*0.0572394324 + 2*0.0572000864 + 0.1263982144) / 6 = 1.207635\n\nThus, the approximate solution of the initial value problem at t = 0.5 using the fourth-order Runge-Kutta method with a step size of 0.1 is y(0.5) â‰ˆ 1.207635."
